# Beat // #003-C

## Nightfall

*"I always told you I had another ace up my sleeve."*


# Objectives

- 5th Ace is taken down, cored out through the hull, no chance of pilot survival.
- The party, sans Harriet are taken captive, but Faun finds a way out.
- A commotion in the bay reveals the Company Resolute have discovered a spy.

---

> Peyton Bay falls. The MABE squad is taken captive, all but Harriet who is either  missing or dead.
> Night falls, a commotion in the newly taken fortress reveals a spy in the Baronic ranks.